PREPARE gelatin as directed on package. Refrigerate 4 hours or until firm. Break gelatin into small flakes with fork. Spoon about 1/2 cup gelatin into each of 8 tall glasses. Pour 1/2 cup cold soft drink over gelatin in each glass. Serve immediately with a straw to sip gelatin pieces and soft drink. Two Color Goo: Prepare 1 pkg. (4-serving size) each grape and orange flavor gelatin as directed on package. Refrigerate and break into flakes as directed. Layer 1/4 cup each orange and grape gelatin flakes in each glass. Pour 1/2 cup cold soft drink over gelatin in each glass. Fizzy Goblin Goo: Just before serving, prepare KOOL-AID as directed, substituting cold seltzer for water.